##Oral Record | Wuhan to Shanghai Dad said: Who Come to want people, you will hand me over!

Micro-signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

People all over the "Wuhan People" of fear and abuse can not bear to read, fear is far more than the virus of the disease.

Dictation | Huang Zheng
Organize East Kim Hee

Dictation | Huang Zheng

Organize East Kim Hee

I am from Wuhan. I have come to Shanghai for more than ten years after graduation. I have settled down in Shanghai for seven years. Since my wife and I are busy with work, my parents have come from Wuhan to help with the children since last summer.

In January, parents and their children spent eight days in Wuhan

My mother, a former public official, retired four years ago, but the activities of the party group of retired cadres are still not left behind. At the beginning of January this year, the original unit informed the Organization of a study conference, and my parents decided to temporarily return to Han for a week to participate in study and handle some chores by the way. At this time although Wuhan spread the news of pneumonia, but the news quickly refuted rumors, as a party member for many years, parents naturally did not particularly care. Although I have concerns, but for many years living in Han, Wuhan's scientific research and medical standards have considerable confidence, discourage fruitless can only advise attention to protection.

The parents arrived in Han with their children on January 13 and were ready to return to Shanghai after finishing. The news broke on January 20 that the situation had taken a turn for the worse, with parents and children returning to Shanghai on the afternoon of January 21, when the circle of Friends of classmates and friends in Wuhan was still optimistic.

When they returned home, the parents said they were fine and wore masks the whole time, but planned to isolate themselves for a week just in case. We don't have a second suite, but at least we have our own room to live in. I told my parents not to go out, to stock up on supplies online, and my wife and I planned to go out early and stay out late, avoiding contact, for the last two working days before the holiday.

On the morning of January 23, I got up to see the news of the city closure in Wuhan. The atmosphere was suddenly tense. The news was very grim. In addition to advising my parents on the matter of separation, my wife and I also began to think about the follow-up issues.

The first problem is the material reserve, near the Spring Festival, the logistics is not smooth, previously ordered protective supplies are still on the way, the inventory of household disinfectant, masks, disposable gloves are still some, can be short-term support, the focus is food reserves. My wife and I quickly divided the work, ordering everything from boxes of horse, jd.com, ele.me, rice, flour, oil, vegetables, meat, eggs, frozen food, canned food, and my in-laws'share, after a morning of struggle, look at the "merchant stock" of the words a little bit more reassuring. At night, when the fridge and shelves were full and the parents and daughter were warm and in good spirits, we relaxed a little.

We decided to isolate ourselves until the end of the holiday and have a peaceful Spring Festival while staying at home.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Homemade dumplings during quarantine

House-to-house quarantine

On New Year's Eve, the original reunion dinner turned into a separate meal, with no taste of the new year, and the New Year greeting atmosphere in the circle of friends was not as good as usual. Most of the time I was greeting my classmates on Wechat and in Han. Fortunately, everyone was safe and sound. I was waiting for the red envelope to be snatched in the evening between jokes.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
A puzzle I spent some time doing during quarantine

Suddenly, the owner of the group sent a picture, posted downstairs neighborhood notice, asked Hubei to return to Shanghai staff report immediately.

Should I report it? Will the whole family be quarantined after the report? I'm having second thoughts.

After discussing it with my wife, I decided to report it to the Neighborhood Committee for help, and my parents agreed. I quickly contacted Xu, the deputy secretary of the residents'committee, on Wechat to let me know what was going on. She quickly returned my call, registered specific information, thanked my family for actively supporting the work of the residents'committee, and announced the policy of home segregation.

After a little peace of mind, I was ready to watch a movie for entertainment, and suddenly found the owner of Wechat Group Fried Pot.

Some of the owners'group said that there were people from Wuhan who returned to Shanghai in the residential area, and there were owners who rose quickly, and after going through all kinds of dark history of the property, they began to complain; the residents'committee cadres began to reassure the owners, saying that they were already registering people from Wuhan who returned to Shanghai, and they were all being isolated at home at present, as a result, the owners are even more worried, have asked to announce the room number, and even put forward to let Wuhan back to Shanghai families to leave the community outside isolation.

I understand the concerns of the owners, in the face of this dangerous epidemic, we are facing unknown risks are panic, just want to protect themselves and their families. I called teacher Xu, and added the Neighborhood Committee secretary's Wechat, asked them to protect our information, but also reiterated that we will consciously quarantine.

After the phone call, the alumni group came from all over again blocked Wuhan back to the local personnel information, inexplicable fear surfaced in the heart.

I told my parents about the reaction of the owners and told them about the quarantine again, only to find that this information had completely triggered the old man's pent-up emotions of many days, tension, anxiety, grievance and anger. Father says: no matter who comes to want a person, you hand me over! I soothed him at once: No one will come for you, and no one will let you out! Shanghai's policy is home segregation with housing. You can't go out now. It's only legal to stay home.

On New Year's Eve, I couldn't sleep because I kept repeating in my head Paul's line from Dune, "fear is the killer of the soul. " .

On the morning of the first day of the Lunar New Year, my parents calmed down a little. My wife and I continued to snap up food on the boxes. At noon, the hospital sent a doctor to the house to take our temperature. He told us to take our temperature twice a day, and took three copies of the letter of commitment on home quarantine. He told us the quarantine method and contact method. After repeated instructions, he also comforted us, after the registration only good no harm, any problem neighborhood committee and the community will help.

Before leaving, the doctor praised the isolation measures of our family, such as separating Wuhan family members in separate rooms, eating separately, opening windows to ventilate and keeping the house empty, which was more scientific than other families visited. "It's the young people who are more aware. "

As the family were in good health, we settled down a little. In the evening, the Neighborhood Committee teacher Xu called to inquire about the situation, the neighborhood committee officers have not rest, she took the initiative to report to our family thanks, they also need to continue house-to-house investigation, the workload is huge.

On the 2nd and 3rd day of the Eighth Lunar Month, my anxiety remained the same. Apart from working in the work group, I didn't seem to do any recreational activities, I couldn't read a book, I wasn't in the mood for watching a movie, and I was worried about whether I would be too tired to affect my resistance. The wechat group was filled with anxiety, all I can do is eat a few more chips to calm my nerves.

The doctor comes to the House twice a day to take your temperature, and every time you take the temperature, you will have a big test. The atmosphere at home was tense, and a cough made my heart skip a beat, even though most of it was just my daughter choking on water.

On the fourth day, my wife and I realized we couldn't go on like this. Wake up in the morning in the box immediately after the dish, began to clean, 84 disinfectant smell people have a strange sense of peace of mind. With the passage of time, the danger will be far away, express delivery and supplies in close proximity to us, we are more and more confident, the mood gradually improved.

Suddenly, the owners of the group fried again, a courier confirmed the news of the field aroused the voice of the block community, although the Group of young people in the opposition, but eventually the Industry Committee decided to take delivery and express blocked at the door, asking the owners to go to the gate.

The original express delivery to the door, I later brought in, no contact with each other. But Express can not enter a community, I can not go out to take again, did not have what to do of supply? Anxiety strikes again.

A friendly neighbor offers a bag of potatoes and Greens at our door, but it's not a good idea to always bother the neighbors. Fortunately, soon the residents'committee cadre coordinated the property to help our family to deliver specially, the security teacher undertook the last several dozen meters to send. Then a few days, years ago ordered express arrival, security master every day take the trouble to run a few times delivery, let us very moved, also some embarrassed, so control two days order.

Near the 10th, parents more calm, father at home every day to ride a dynamic bicycle, push-up, mother is to play a set of Tai Chi Chuan. But as I approached the exam, I became even more nervous. Half because of their own situation, the other half is for the home situation, fragmentary information shows the devastation of Wuhan, people everywhere "Wuhan People" fear and abuse, fear is far worse than the virus disease.

De-quarantine and remain closed

The 10th day, 14 days like a year, finally arrived, the hospital sent to lift the quarantine notice, we quickly to the neighborhood, kindergarten photos, neighborhood cadres and kindergarten teachers in the same happy mood as us.

However, the self isolation is not over, the virus is rampant, we do not dare to go out, I asked the family members still closed in the home, except no longer bother the security master to take express delivery, garbage, nothing else changes.

Once, after watching movies like Resident Evil and 10 Cloverfield Lane, I also imagined the end of the world as a home for instant noodles and video games. It seemed like a good idea, but the reality came so quickly, for more than half a month, there was no sign of relief. When this epidemic ends, the pressure on the economy, on jobs, on incomes, on countries, on families, on ourselves, is going to be a mountain. During the isolation period, I would like to thank my family, especially my wife, for their understanding and support. I would also like to thank the residents, local hospitals and security teachers for their help.

Now, Beijing and Shanghai Alumni group one after another from their own or their families to lift the quarantine message, but the situation is still grim, as if the unknown future has come to us. But I believe that the epidemic will be overcome.
